WEBVTT

00:00:00.001 --> 00:00:02.953
"Fruit"

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.113
(Mom: Are you going to
send me living expenses or not?)

00:00:10.630 --> 00:00:13.100
(Episode 6: Sun)

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:16.100
Hey little guy, why are you out here all alone?

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:17.766
You're completely soaked.

00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.666
Let me find something to cover you up.

00:00:19.666 --> 00:00:20.966
Don't go running off, okay?

00:00:20.966 --> 00:00:22.700
I'll come see you again tomorrow.

00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:27.366
Let's not smother him with towels.

00:00:27.926 --> 00:00:29.570
That day,

00:00:29.570 --> 00:00:32.493
I met my sun in the rain.

00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:34.313
Miss...

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:36.200
They'll trap the moisture.

00:00:44.966 --> 00:00:46.600
What's it called?

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:48.266
Does it have a name?

00:00:49.733 --> 00:00:50.633
No.

00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:55.166
How about

00:00:55.166 --> 00:00:57.400
"Chips"?

00:00:57.400 --> 00:00:59.500
Don't you think it looks like...

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:00.861
Like...

00:01:00.861 --> 00:01:01.947
Like snacks?

00:01:01.947 --> 00:01:02.933
Right, exactly!

00:01:02.933 --> 00:01:04.333
Just like snacks!

00:01:04.333 --> 00:01:07.133
From now on, your name is Chips.

00:01:07.133 --> 00:01:08.266
In that moment,

00:01:09.300 --> 00:01:11.700
I felt my heartbeat quicken,

00:01:12.700 --> 00:01:14.700
but I immediately told myself

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:16.466
it was an illusion.

00:01:21.282 --> 00:01:22.564
Chips.

00:01:29.166 --> 00:01:30.800
Keep the umbrella.

00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:31.817
Don't catch a cold.

00:01:36.800 --> 00:01:37.700
Miss.

00:01:38.900 --> 00:01:41.066
So will you come again tomorrow?

00:01:43.800 --> 00:01:45.666
I have to be here every day.

00:01:45.666 --> 00:01:47.933
After going back that day,

00:01:47.933 --> 00:01:50.400
I listened to the rain.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:52.566
It was like a heartbeat,

00:01:52.566 --> 00:01:54.566
reminding me

00:01:54.566 --> 00:01:56.466
not to fall for that smile.

00:02:31.700 --> 00:02:32.833
The outlines are too rigid.

00:02:33.666 --> 00:02:35.208
You're peeking at me drawing.

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:38.814
I'm looking at the paper.

00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:42.833
Relax your hand.

00:02:44.066 --> 00:02:45.266
Leave some space for the light.

00:02:48.525 --> 00:02:49.525
Meanie.

00:02:52.035 --> 00:02:53.600
Don't rush to layer it.

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:57.500
Find the shadows first... then build it up.

00:02:59.966 --> 00:03:00.833
Maybe,

00:03:01.666 --> 00:03:04.066
I shouldn't have kept this image in my heart.

00:03:07.539 --> 00:03:08.958
What about the shadow?

00:03:14.166 --> 00:03:14.966
Class dismissed.

00:03:16.933 --> 00:03:18.433
I'll tell you next time.

00:03:32.243 --> 00:03:36.133
Light is a...

00:03:36.133 --> 00:03:37.666
If I could decide the light,

00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:41.433
I would want it to shine on us.

00:03:42.566 --> 00:03:44.166
But the reality is...

00:03:45.533 --> 00:03:48.766
I must hide in the darkness, undiscovered.

00:03:48.766 --> 00:03:50.732
Everyone, that's all

00:03:50.732 --> 00:03:51.676
for today.

00:04:17.785 --> 00:04:23.126
(Mom: If you're really too busy,
I'll just go back to the doctor myself.)

00:04:28.966 --> 00:04:30.566
I'll go over tomorrow.

00:05:01.266 --> 00:05:02.700
Hello, Mom.

00:05:03.700 --> 00:05:04.633
Yeah.

00:05:06.200 --> 00:05:09.100
Don't go out by yourself, it's dangerous.

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:11.198
I'll be over tomorrow morning.

00:05:11.198 --> 00:05:12.198
Yeah.

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:34.071
This exhaustion...

00:05:34.071 --> 00:05:36.500
when will it ever end?

00:06:05.412 --> 00:06:07.932
I thought I was already used to the dark.

00:06:09.966 --> 00:06:11.833
Until she appeared.

00:06:13.700 --> 00:06:15.200
Like a ray of sunlight,

00:06:16.466 --> 00:06:18.633
quietly spilling into my heart.

00:06:35.214 --> 00:06:37.616
(Heping University Hospital)
(NTD 134,023)

00:06:37.616 --> 00:06:42.026
(To be continued...)

00:06:42.757 --> 00:06:50.792
(Next...)